{"page":1,"results":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":4310251,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Artem Lytvynenko","original_name":"Artem Lytvynenko","popularity":0.0673,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/6N3HOPI6uQcqUTcboQ3t1ECHoIE.jpg","id":236654,"name":"The First Days","original_name":"He jotka jäivät","overview":"A unique drama anthology series for our time, inspired by true events which happened in Kyiv in the first few weeks after the Russian invasion of Ukraine in February 2022. As the brutal war got underway, every second person left Kyiv. Yet every second person remained. These are their stories – variously moving, funny, sad, stark, unsettling, and uplifting.","poster_path":"/gpKMV0oZphbyW2O1WYhGLt6Rtv8.jpg","media_type":"tv","original_language":"fi","genre_ids":[18,10768],"popularity":0.5111,"first_air_date":"2023-10-29","softcore":false,"vote_average":7.4,"vote_count":5,"origin_country":["FI"]},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"id":1566982,"title":"The Drive","original_title":"На драйві","overview":"A group of friends in frontline Kharkiv discovers abandoned cars inside a war-shuttered shopping mall and turns them into the core of an underground racing scene. What begins as an escape from reality quickly becomes a rule-free game powered by bets, clout, and danger. As adrenaline and social-media fame escalate, every race could be their last, and the stakes now include friendship, trust, and holding on to who they are.","poster_path":"/AtjfaxHTAlKSQfVuaM4tHUy0CpL.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"uk","genre_ids":[12,28,18,10749,10752],"popularity":0.4608,"release_date":"2026-04-09","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":8.0,"vote_count":1}]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1575915,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Artem Lytvynenko","original_name":"Artyom Litvinenko","popularity":0.0214,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"id":371879,"title":"Beyond","original_title":"По той бік","overview":"Death, which did not happen – it's just the beginning. Iryna miraculously survived after an accident. Facing death changed her forever. From time to time, Iryna started to see visions. They were short fragments episodes, fragmentary images. She couldn't understand it, and how does this relate to her. Over time, she learned to analyze what is happening in her head, and it started to bear fruit. Iryna began to solve the crime scenes. This is a story that is dangerously balancing on the edge of life and death, reality and dreaming, white lie and killing truth. A story that will change forever the fate of the inhabitants of a small town.","poster_path":"/xx8pwYF0YR7p7PWsrjdupQloj09.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"uk","genre_ids":[80,53,9648],"popularity":0.2242,"release_date":"2015-12-03","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.0,"vote_count":2}]}],"total_pages":1,"total_results":2}